Useful command lines:
    `grunt watch`
    `sass --watch sass:css`
    `browser-sync start --proxy localhost/vps/web/ --files="**/*.css, **/*.html, **/*.php, **/.htaccess"`

# Install
To run the application, first of all install `node`, `npm`, `git` and a web serveur (LAMP)

Initialize the project if needed:
    `grunt init`
    `bower init`

Then, install necessary software to work on the project:
    `npm install -g grunt-cli`
    `npm install -g bower`
    `npm install` (will browse the package.json file to install all dependencies)

